headline: Tenet Healthcare Beats Q4 Earnings: But 2026 EBITDA Margin May Decline
summary: THC tops Q4 estimates with strong EBITDA growth, but 2026 guidance midpoint hints at a potential margin dip despite a higher revenue outlook.

headline: Tenet expects $250M hit from loss of ACA subsidies this year
summary: Still, the for-profit hospital operator’s projected loss is less than some of its peers, and Tenet said it expected to grow its earnings in 2026.
